ch.grengine.code

Interface Code

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SingleSourceCode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultCode, DefaultSingleSourceCode

    public interface Code
    Interface for code from compiling an instance of Sources.

    Contains bytecode and class names, as well as information related to the originating sources.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alain Stalder, Made in Switzerland.
